event: message_saved
data: {"messageId":"T65dON3cFXhvcvo1WB-Pq","role":"user","content":"I need you to conduct deep research on 'FedRAMP Authorization for AI/ML Systems in 2025-2026' and synthesize actionable findings. Here's the workflow:\n\n1. Use web_search to find the latest FedRAMP guidance for AI/ML systems. Search for at least 3 different queries:\n   - 'FedRAMP AI ML authorization 2025 2026'\n   - 'NIST AI Risk Management Framework FedRAMP'\n   - 'FedRAMP Moderate baseline AI systems requirements'\n\n2. Use web_fetch on the top 2 most relevant URLs from your search results to get detailed content.\n\n3. Use web_verify_fact to check: 'FedRAMP requires continuous monitoring for AI/ML model drift'\n\n4. Use web_store_knowledge to save a structured summary of the key FedRAMP requirements for AI systems.\n\n5. Use admin_system_postgres_raw_query to check how many knowledge entries exist in the system: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM \"ChatMessage\" WHERE role = 'assistant'\n\n6. Synthesize everything into a structured report with:\n   - Key FedRAMP requirements specific to AI/ML\n   - Gap analysis for an enterprise agentic platform\n   - Recommended remediation timeline\n   - Risk ratings (Critical/High/Medium/Low)\n\nThis is a REAL research task - use the actual tools, don't make up the findings.","timestamp":"2026-02-20T21:54:26.787Z","source":"database","confirmed":true}

